<placeName cert="high">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Θεωνᾶς Τεθεῦτι τῆι μητρὶ καὶ κυρίᾳ πλεῖστα <expan>χαί<ex cert="high">ρειν</ex></expan>. 

    <lb n="2"/><choice><corr>γινώσκειν</corr><sic>γεινωσκειν</sic></choice> σ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ε</supplied> θέλω ὅτι διὰ τοσούτου χρόνου οὐκ ἀ-

    <lb n="3"/>πέσταλκά σοι ἐπιστόλιον διότι ἐν παρεμβολῇ <choice><corr>εἰμι</corr><sic>ημι</sic></choice> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">καὶ</unclear> 

    <lb n="4"/>οὐ δι᾽ ἀσθένε<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ι</supplied>αν, ὥστε μὴ <choice><corr>λυποῦ</corr><sic>λοιπ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ου</unclear></sic></choice>. <choice><corr>λίαν</corr><sic>λειαν</sic></choice> δ᾽ <choice><corr>ἐλυπήθην</corr><sic>ελοιπηθη<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear></sic></choice> 

    <lb n="5"/>ἀκούσας ὅτι ἤκουσας. οὐ γὰρ δ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ειν</unclear>ῶς ἠσθένησα. μέμ-

    <lb n="6"/>φομαι δὲ τὸν εἴπαντα σοι. μὴ ὀχλοῦ δὲ πέμπειν τι ἡ-

    <lb n="7"/>μῖν. ἐκομισάμεθα δὲ τὰ θαλλία παρὰ <app type="BL"><lem resp="4.62">τοῦ τοῦ</lem><rdg>τοῦ <sic>τοῦ</sic></rdg></app> Ἡρακλεί-

    <lb n="8"/>δου. Διονυτᾶς δὲ ὁ ἀδελφός μου ἤνεγκέ μοι τὸν θαλ-

    <lb n="9"/>λὸν κα<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὶ τὴν</supplied> ἐπιστολήν <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">σου</supplied> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἐ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">κο</supplied>μι<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σά</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">μ</supplied>ην. εὐχαριστῶ 

    <lb n="10"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τοῖς θεοῖς </supplied><gap extent="13" reason="lost" unit="character"/> πά<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear>τοτε, <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἐ</unclear>π<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear>κ<gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ε</unclear><gap extent="2" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear>α 

    <lb n="11"/><gap extent="22" reason="lost" unit="character"/>ν<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ται</unclear> δη<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λῶ</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ο</unclear>υ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">π</unclear><gap extent="3" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">αυ</unclear>-

    <lb n="12"/><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="line"/> 
</ab></div><div n="r,ms" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="12" rend="perpendicular"/> μὴ ἐπιβαροῦ πέμπειν τι ἡμῖν τω<gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> 
